[audit_log_hashchain]
Processes input:
    - event_id: string (event identifier)
    - prev_hash: string (SHA2-512 hexadecimal previous hash)
Generates output:
    - current_hash: string (new hash value)
Implements protocol (hashing mechanism):
    - Hashes using SHA2-512 (secure hash algorithm 2-512, NIST certified)
    - Chains via append-only, time/clock verified secure ledger (immutable record)
Sets dest-path: /infra/audit_trails/daily/${event_id}/
Enforces logging:
    - Ensures compliance with SOX, ISO/IEC 27001
    - Stores logs at: /infra/audit_trails/daily/
Manages lifecycle: 7+ year immutable retention, compliance export features
Enforces security_policy: tamperproof chain integrity, export readiness
